name: Ciara O'Doherty
description:
An updated embedding of Instagrammer, fashion influencer and star of the Try Channel on YouTube Ciara O'Doherty.

Works pretty well at strength 1, the necklace was pretty much omnipresent in the training data so will need negative prompting out if you don't want it.

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Based on 60 images from her Instagram and promotional shoots etc.

Much improved, much more detailed than v1.0.

25,000 steps, Learning rate of 0.0015, 12 vectors per token

Example images all run using a standard prompt with outfit and background changes only. Did not generate any images that were not clearly her, nor any eldritch horrors.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description:
This is only my third TI, but I followed various online advice and used settings suggested by @Bozack3000 - turned out a lot better than expected.

An embedding of Instagrammer and star of the Try Channel on YouTube Ciara O'Doherty.

Based on 23 images from her IG. Works pretty well at strength 1, the necklace was omnipresent in the training data so will need negative prompting out if you don't want it.
